Comment: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP end}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no Shakespeare play,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but to stay or to leave—that is the question \Nfor our High Collar Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorant of how she feels, \NRanmaru and Ushigorou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,launched a spirited all-out offensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,rendering the poor hard-working \Nhead maid Kisaragi down for the count.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it appears Shinobu had finally unmasked Ranmaru, even if he keeps playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady struggles to guess \Nwhat Shinobu's true intentions are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one worry after another for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off! It's my turn this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm polishing it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to look after \NYoung Master's belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Young Master chose me to do it! {no clue whats this se}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.43,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you both want to polish them so badly, \Nwhy not polish one each?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that could actually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is shinier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies! Mine is sparkling!{嘘、私の方がぴかぴかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should trust others \Nto take care of Shinobu's things, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio, are you listening?{ねえ紅緒さんってば}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! I'd rather be taking care \Nof my buddy right here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,than of someone like Shinobu!{a more direct wording for what she probably means: "this knight armor is dearer to me than shinobu" though I don't properly remember the context}{あんな人の世話をするくらいなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, I understand how you feel!{わかるわかるその気持ち}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Attagirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That sublieutenant doesn't care about me in the slightest...{私のこと何とも思っていないshouiなんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:01.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\c&HF1E6E4&\pos(720,100)\bord0\blur1\fs60\b1}Episode 14\N{\fs100}Two Bewildered Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L-L-Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, p-please don't worry!{ご心配ごめんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reassemble it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, this looks like a foot, I think...{これが足}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio! Forget about this junk and show at least some solicitude for Young Master!{Benio-sama!少しは若様の身の回りをお世話して差し上げなければ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Who cares about him...{誰が少尉なんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.{いいよいいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll do it myself.{では私が代わりに}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? How pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pads also didn't flee to your back today. Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember and appreciate \Nyour samurai-like lenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where are my gloves?{手袋は}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what negligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, hurry up and bring them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait.{あ待ちなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} job!{あなたのお仕事です}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Young Master's gloves here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. What's the big deal \Nwith just bringing the gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Ah, here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually! I wonder how he'd react \Nif I gave him two right-hand ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's give it a whirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She is rather late. \NWhy is it taking so long?{遅いわね何してるのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.{では}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return soon, Young Master!{いってらっしゃいませ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How boring. He didn't even \Ntry them on before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?{それどういうこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like playing a prank on Shinobu, so I gave him two right-hand gloves! Look, here are the left ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as usual!{やるんさすが}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! With a little luck, that might embarrass him big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, Shinobu is supposed to be a standard-bearer.{伊集院少尉は確か連隊旗手だったんじゃねえんですかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, \Nmy father once mentioned that too.{そういえばお父様が以前そんなことおっしゃってたわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's a standard-bearer?{ねぇねぇ連隊旗手って何}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute His Majesty the Emperor.{賢くも天皇陛下から賜った}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease.{休め}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one holding the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare! {/Salute the flag!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the regiment, only the most accomplished young officers can become standard-bearers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be one, you need to wear your white gloves at all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So if someone like that forgets his gloves...{じゃあ手袋を忘れたとなれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Exactly what you think of!{まず間違いなく}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His district commander will have him for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And since your father is Shinobu's direct superior,\Nhe's also getting the shaft for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's that big of a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be any other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now{\i0} Benio is getting the boot for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hip hip, hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?\NShinobu, that's not what I had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, what's wrong? \NYou've been sighing so gloomily all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... It's nothing.{何でもないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your glove mischief should've taken effect by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, you'll be able to bid your farewell to that mansion, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop all of a sudden?{何を急に止まったりして}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what we got... {dunno what he's saying}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do those three want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey!{いやいやいやい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a public road, \Nso why don'tcha get out of our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that lady who's engaged to sublieutenant Ijuuin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We are...{あしらは}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the most influential gang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the whole Kanto district!{縄張りをもつやくざ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Say our name out loud,{その名も高き}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilac Band!{すみれ組 - sumire/violet squad}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilac Band...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Stop, stop! Ushigorou, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so then you guys must be \Nthe part of the Lilac Theater Troupe! {/Oh, so then you guys must be singing the violet song!; すみれ組のさんしただから - not really sure, don't know what sanshita is supposed to mean}{i suspect sumire gumi is a parody of some real theater troupe, also kindergarten groups seem to be often named "flower-gumi"; sanshita could be "underlings" or "three [something]", none of which makes much sense; kichij's instituion later is called "house of flowers" so maybe it's some organization that overlooks the geisha cafes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, our beloved troupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pam-pa-bam...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When the lilacs... {https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%86%8D%E3%81%B3%E7%99%BD%E3%81%84%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A9%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF%E3%81%8C%E5%92%B2%E3%81%84%E3%81%9F%E3%82%89_(%E6%9B%B2)}{lyrics from https://youtu.be/n0rW4K8UuXw?si=EnZxYb_xVXd2c6pJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When the lilacs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,bloom again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing back the thrill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! You think it's time to be singing our theme song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!{笑うじゃねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing personal against you two, \Nbut I gotta make a living somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, we'll have to hurt you a bit.{ちっとばかり痛い目にあっていただきやす}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What do you mean by that?!{なんですってどういうわけで}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No arguing! Get off!{問答無用降りよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you want to fight me? {/telling me to get off}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks to me like you ain't deaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did get off, so I'm no longer responsible \Nfor whatever happens to you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight with your fists, \Nnot your mouth, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch! {literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss, don't underestimate them. \NThese guys rule the streets down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So what of it?{それがどうしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Provoking me today was a bad idea, \Nso I'll use them to let off some steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll be facing you!{よし俺が相手だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that it was you who started all of this!{喧嘩売ったのはそっちだってこと覚えといてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ya gon' teach me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!{やった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! I don't have all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This wench! I went easy on her 'cause she's a woman!{このあま女だと思って手加減してやったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get serious!{勘弁ならねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch!{めろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,B-B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, Ushigorou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know why, \Nbut I've not been this excited in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rot in...{地獄へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hell!{落ちろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.38,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.93,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{fuck this}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally.{やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight to hell.{地獄行き}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'll let yakuza scum like you \Nget the best of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!{おやめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you, \Ngoing three against one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were concerned about you...{しかしあしらは姉さんの気持ちを}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do things I haven't asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember ever hiring you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. She's pretty. \NAnd also so strong-willed!{美人！それにすんごい迫力}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, milady,\Nthese thugs keep troubling my acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a geisha from Yanagibashi,\NKichiji of the "House of Flowers."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! So you are the Sister Kichiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you are Hanamura Benio?{嬢さんはhanamura benio様}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... How do you know me, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I happen to be in love...{この吉次はね伊集院の若様に}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in love?{若様に}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With Sublieutenant Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's purely one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's clear to me that I stand no chance of getting his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if {\i1}you{\i0} are his fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not like that. A-Actually, \Nwe aren't officially married yet...{まだ婚約なんて正式じゃないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Shinobu is not really interested in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?{何をおっしゃいます}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It is plain to the eye \Nthat you have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to you, what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A geisha cannot dare to dream about ever being with a nobleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I did start to think about breaking off his engagement, if only I get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, until I unexpectedly met you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady.{お嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of Sublieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kichiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that shameless womanizer!{まああの女性の敵}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu had also been fooling around with that geisha behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! Un-bloody-forgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A single sneeze...\NI hope it's not a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come so suddenly... I don't suppose \Nit's because something happened to Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd be lying if I said \Nthat nothing at all happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is unbearable. To think that she would lose her chance for such a great engagement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him.\NI won't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in a thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.{おかえりなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what's wrong?{紅生さんどうしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, today's the day. \NHelp me pack my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already done that in foresight.{そう来ると思ってもうまとめてあるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you a clairvoyant?{えっあんた千里眼なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With you, even the telepathy \Nis not impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, I was just kidding. \NAnyways, I'll get your things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that pile?{何をそれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell? It's today's share of love letters for Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like this every day!{毎日これだもんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a playboy before!{あんなプレイボーイ見たことないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Author, seriously?! \NEven you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.079087\fscx100.64\fscy118.22\frz-16.4768\frx0.4942\fry-1.9812\xbord4.11\ybord4.73\org(1111.63,476.78)\pos(1117.6,388.12)\c&H2B373D&\3c&HE2DEDD&}Dear Shinobu \N\NI'm head over heels for you~{seems like mairu to me, though I'm unsure} \N\N\N\N\N\N \h   ♥Waki{it's the manga author's name - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waki_Yamato ; another reading is "Kazunori"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not staying here for a second longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... He's late, isn't he?{遅いなもう}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait a second.{待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell Shinobu \Njust one thing before we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You still can't let go of a man like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that. I just wanted to give him \Na piece of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. A piece it is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get into trouble because of the gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hearing what I'm hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was very inconsiderate of me.{少尉あれは私が悪いんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't embarrass you before your unit, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... We actually just laughed it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it turns out \Nthe world is full of scatterbrains,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so another officer happened to bring two left-handed gloves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I exchanged my right glove with his left one,\Nand we both made it through alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,can you guess who this officer \Nwith two left-hand gloves actually was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,None other than your father!{benioさんのお父上の花村少佐}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was probably a slip-up on your Nanny's part, \Nbecause her mind was preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you left, your Nanny must've been feeling lonely, and that was slowly consuming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how she made that slip-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on my way back, I stopped by at your house to comfort your Nanny for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your self-aggrandizement... {/that much of ostensible kindness}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm not falling for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about his womanizing exploits! {lit: I have all the evidence}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny asked me to give something to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is for you, Ranmaru-not, Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a lot. \NAre those all love letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be joking. \NIt's just the fan mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never answer to any of these, \Nbut they still keep writing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel you, every day is like that for me.{僕のところへも毎日来るんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who's sending them, \Nit's all one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? One-sided?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! He's so pretentious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are for Benio, \None from Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:15.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.278920\fscx74.85\fscy103.86\frz-30.4265\frx14.9485\fry3.4998\xbord3.06\ybord4.15\org(971.63,486.87)\pos(982.07,434.94)\c&H2F484F&\3c&HCDCFCF&}To Benio \Nfrom Saburou
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.584424\fscx85.66\fscy123.01\frz-29.4295\frx13.5148\fry-0.1222\xbord3.49\ybord4.92\org(335.79,379.94)\pos(373.33,287.68)\c&H2A4254&\3c&HD4D3D6&}To \NYoung  \h\NMistress      \h
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's from Sabu and Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?{何者です}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two kids in my neighborhood.{近所の小学生なるほど}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I didn't expect a letter from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Benio, let's climb trees \Ntogether again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Climbing trees?{木登り}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Hiroshi write?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Benio, when are you coming back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't wait to climb a tree!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never forget the trees we climbed together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Hiroshi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? \NHe only cares about climbing trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The letters for me are completely down to earth. \NFan mail is stupid! {lit: so un-sexy for me/uncolorful}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,{nah}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to turn away when laughing! {hope she means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.{いや失礼}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna keep on laughing forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know your true colors, and about your affair with Ms. Kichiji from the House of Flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've met her?{彼女に会ったんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your expression changed!{顔色が変わった}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...{彼女は}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong on her account, Benio.{違いますそんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't misunderstand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me your lame excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people like you \Nwho play with women's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Out, out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a nominal fiancée,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,shanghaied into a loveless marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much to bear!{これじゃあんまりひどすぎる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Being made into a figurehead wife \Nwho resigned to her husband's adultery
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,without hope of ever getting a divorce,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,working herself to the bone just to quietly \Nperish in the most miserable way—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:30.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.021572\fscx67.27\fscy69.33\frz1.1746\frx-4.3929\fry-1.0417\xbord2.74\ybord2.77\org(1282.71,103.83)\move(1700,50,1280,50,0,650)\c&H35484F&\3c&HE6DCD4&}For some reason, \Nchildren are the only thing \Nwe have a lot of {なぜか子供だけはたくさんいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,such is the sad fate of womankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've decided! \NDown with this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H243239&\3c&HD9D2CE&\fs100}To Young Mistress
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Nanny?{バーヤの手紙}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Young Mistress, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for myself, I am living peacefully, all alone with your father.{私は旦那様と二人っきりでのんびりしています}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has never expressed any anxiety about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand how you might be feeling, \Nbut please never consider returning home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:22:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, I have never had the wish \Nto see you again either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I beg you not to come back home, \Nno matter what happens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never, never come back home, please.{\i0}{決して 決して戻らないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never, never come back home, please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In our world, things always have two sides to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should still try to loosen the knots on the tangled thread of a heart that's been smashed to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you succeed, it'll bloom again... {no idea what's this about, seems to be a very convoluted philosophical parable}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But with which flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,During the airing of old family possessions,{伊集院家の古い品物の虫干しで}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,something slips from Ranmaru's hand and breaks,{蘭丸が手を滑らせてポロリと割った皿1枚}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and, oh goodness, it was a precious plate!{なんとこれが大事な果報のお皿}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Count obviously snaps out and draws his katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, to give the remaining nine plates the same fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio decides to break all of them! Big trouble!{紅葉がお皿全部を叩き割ったからさ大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on "Here Comes the High Collar Lady":
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So Long, Old-Fashioned Mansion! Don't miss it!{さようなら、古きものよ！お楽しみに}
Comment: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
